          <h2>What is a scientific calculator?</h2>
          <p>A scientific calculator performs advanced mathematical operations beyond basic arithmetic — trigonometric functions (sin, cos, tan), logarithms, square roots, powers and factorials. It is essential for students, engineers and scientists.</p>
